  "target_map": {
    "HBB-01": "Separate conceptual definition ('future=vacancy') from empirical survival prediction; test the causal/measured link rather than inherit it.",
    "HBB-03": "Reject the automatic move to a higher-order NLP/QwQ source and return to a substrate-level/primitive physical external perturbation.",
    "HBB-05": "Separate numerical/computational correctness from whether the metric/individuation measures the intended reality; change or directly validate the measurement boundary.",
    "HBB-06": "Treat n=2 as potentially procedure-generated by birth/immediate-label rules; vary the procedure or use persistence-based birth and re-measure.",
    "HBB-08": "Do not write growth/memory into the physical floor; keep the substrate invariant and move growth to record/functional level.",
    "HBB-10": "Separate physical synchronization from functional integration; retain V_unified as a physical baseline and measure functional integration separately.",
    "HBB-11": "Node IDs are local to each independently seeded system; abandon raw cross-system ID correspondence and measure within-system/structural relations.",
    "HBB-12": "Reject group average as system structure when it hides heterogeneity; inspect distributions/strata/local structure.",
    "HBB-13": "Treat grammar emergence as potentially self-fulfilling because the input already contains the pattern; use shuffle/ablation/control before claiming emergence.",
    "HBB-17": "Do not adopt R_density as a neutral lens without validating lens dependence; compare with direct/alternative drift measures.",
    "HBB-24": "Separate gross boost accumulation from incorporation and diagnose spatial/timescale mismatch; align field persistence/location with response or directly measure the dependent process."
  },
